data.description: Spacious family home with a SALT WATER pool with a brand new well tank, pipes, and pump just put in that supply the pool and the sprinklers! This Milton contemporary is a must see, pictures don't do a justice. This home offers over 2,500 square feet including four bedrooms, two full bathrooms, AND an office!! The interior features a semi-open floor plan with a large great room, formal dining room, and a modern kitchen. The kitchen was recently renovated with stylish two-toned cabinets and a marble look backsplash, plus stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. It also has an adjacent breakfast area that looks out into the grand great room with its cathedral ceilings and wood burning fireplace. One on end of the home are the three guest bedrooms and office which share a hall bathroom. Split from the guest rooms on the opposite side is the private master suite. Its generous size allows space for a king bed set and a sitting area, and it has an amazing ensuite bathroom. The master bath has his and hers walk-in closets and double vanities so you won't have to share with your partner! There is also a water closet for privacy, a soaking tub, and separate shower. Out back is the privacy fenced yard and the inground pool! Just imagine hosting barbecues this summer and diving in the relaxing water to cool off. This is such a great opportunity for a growing family and it won't last long, so schedule a showing today!! Pool liner is 2021. HVAC is 2021. Roof is Oct 2022.
